headline: PH Q4 Deep Dive: Margin Expansion and Filtration Group Acquisition Drive Guidance Increase
summary: Industrial machinery company Parker-Hannifin (NYSE:PH) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 9.1% year on year to $5.17 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $7.65 per share was 6.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
